Class FileList

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections.list.BaseList<Element>
com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections.list.ObjectList<File>
com.telenav.kivakit.filesystem.FileList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Addable<File>, Appendable<File>, Indexable<File>, Prependable<File>, Sequence<File>, Countable, Sized, NewInstance<BaseList<File>>, CompressibleCollection, AsString, Iterable<File>, Collection<File>, List<File>, RandomAccess
public class FileList extends ObjectList<File>
A list of files with useful methods added. Additional methods include:
  • asJavaFiles() - This file list as a list of File objects
  • asSet() - This list as a set
  • Sequence.first() - The first file in this list
  • largest() - The largest file in this list
  • matching(Matcher) - The files in this list matching the given matcher
  • smallest() - The smallest file in this list
  • sortedLargestToSmallest() - This file list sorted
  • sortedLargestToSmallest() - This file list sorted
  • sortedOldestToNewest() ()} - This file list sorted
